response.overview: Deep Space 69: Boner Expansion Pack chronicles the misadventures of a transport ship in outer space led by Jay and his koala bear co-pilot, Hamilton. A send-up to the many humorless sci-fi films and series that take themselves far too seriously, Deep Space 69 treads lightly on space exploration and instead focuses on Jay's incessant exploits with the fairer sex and Hamilton's frustration with their foolish missions.  This DEEP SPACE 69 package features Season 3 of the series: seven episodes rereleased to include uncensored content, plus a never-before-seen uncensored bonus episode. For mature audiences.
